casebody.data:
BRYSON, et al.
v.
ATTORNEY GENERAL, et al. No. 640P04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005.

Lester Daniel Bryson, Pro Se.

William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Attorney General et al.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st day of June 2005 by Plaintiffs to Restrain and to Compel in the above styled case:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 18th day of August 2005."
